  <source>Rambam Health Care Campus</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Weight gain is both a significant risk factor for obstructive sleep apnea and a side-effect
      of long-term systemic steroids therapy.

      This study aimed to investigate the impact of long-term systemic steroid treatment on sleep
      apnea.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
